@page "/"

<PageTitle>仪表盘</PageTitle>

<h1>仪表盘</h1>
<p class="text-muted">对应需求 <strong>2.9 Dashboard</strong>：以下为占位 KPI / 图表区，后续接入报表与图表组件。</p>

<div class="row g-3 mb-4">
    <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-muted small">客户数</div>
                <div class="fs-4">—</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-muted small">订单数</div>
                <div class="fs-4">—</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-muted small">商品数</div>
                <div class="fs-4">—</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-muted small">销售收入</div>
                <div class="fs-4">—</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-muted small">净利润</div>
                <div class="fs-4">—</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row g-3">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">趋势图（月收入 / 净利润）</div>
            <div class="card-body text-muted" style="min-height: 200px;">
                图表占位 — ECharts / EChartsNet（见需求 1.1 / 2.9）
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">按市场/摊位柱状图</div>
            <div class="card-body text-muted" style="min-height: 200px;">
                图表占位
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">占比环图</div>
            <div class="card-body text-muted" style="min-height: 160px;">今日 / 本周 / 本月 / 累计</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">支付方式分布</div>
            <div class="card-body text-muted" style="min-height: 160px;">饼图占位</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
